Package: ipgeolocation
Type: Package
Title: Client for the IPGeolocation.io IP Location API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Anwar", "Ahmed", email = "anwar@jfreaks.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("IPGeolocation", "IO", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Provides functions to query the IPGeolocation.io
    IP Geolocation API and related endpoints. Supports retrieval of
    IP location data (including continent, country, state, city,
    coordinates, EU status, geoname ID, DMA code, locality, accuracy
    radius, confidence, and geo_accuracy), country metadata (calling
    code, TLD, languages), network information (connection type,
    routing, anycast), currency details, ASN data, company
    information, time zone data, and IP abuse contact details.
    Optional objects such as security, hostname, geo_accuracy,
    dma_code, abuse, and user_agent can be requested via the
    'include' parameter (paid plans only). Response filtering is
    supported using the 'fields' and 'excludes' parameters,
    including dot notation for nested objects. Returns parsed API
    responses as R objects.
